::Enertron::
    "As you wish."  As the blasts closed in from both sides he made the only 
logical choice, he launched himself straight up.  As he rose he spun, only 
halting his spin when he was high above the ground by flinging his wings out 
to his sides.  He fired 10 medium powered shots with pinpoint accuracy at 
Galvatron's head.
